==English==

===Etymology===
From the Greek ''holon'' "whole" + ''onoma'' "name"

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[word]] which includes the given part or parts.
#: ''Examples'':
#:: ''body is a holonym of arm, leg and heart''
#:: ''word is a holonym of letter''

